sourcesContent: import React, { Component } from 'react' import { Item } from 'semantic-ui-react' const RelationshipItem = ({user, relationship, selectRelationship}) => { const handleClick = (event) => { selectRelationship(relationship) } return ( {relationship.user.display_name} Matched on: {relationship.created_at} {relationship.user.bio} ) } export default RelationshipItem
